- [Man] Yeah

00:04:52.050 --> 00:04:53.798
- Ah, here they come out right now.

00:04:53.798 --> 00:04:54.798
What a dish!

00:04:57.504 --> 00:04:58.718
Just getting ready to
cook a couple of dishes.

00:04:58.718 --> 00:05:02.135
Fish roe tuna, tuna eggs, tuna roe curry!

00:05:04.283 --> 00:05:06.187
You've got to check out the design on

00:05:06.187 --> 00:05:09.795
