So the charcoal, the
firewood, burn down here.

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:15.429
The clay pot sits above here,

00:05:15.429 --> 00:05:18.256
and then there's airflow on this side.

00:05:18.256 --> 00:05:20.028
Coconut oil.

