The cuttle fish.

00:05:40.531 --> 00:05:41.767
- The boss (laughs).

00:05:41.767 --> 00:05:43.586
This is my mum's oldest sister.

00:05:43.586 --> 00:05:44.786
- Cuttle fish.

00:05:44.786 --> 00:05:46.226
- [Mark] The greatest.

00:05:46.226 --> 00:05:48.809
(upbeat music)

00:05:50.236 --> 00:05:52.486
(sizzling)

